Additionally, the paper mentions various perception tasks, which are typically associated with computer vision. The paper also mentions the use of intrinsic features and extrinsic correlations, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of convolutional networks and deep learning techniques also suggests that it could belong to multimedia (cs.MM) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
